Package: footdata
Type: Package
Title: Load, Process, and Merge Datasets with Footnotes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rania Antonopoulou [aut] (<ran.antonopoulou@gmail.com>)
Maintainer: Rania Antonopoulou <ran.antonopoulou@gmail.com>
Description: The 'footdata' package streamlines handling datasets with footnotes. 
            It enables loading datasets, merging footnotes, and exporting the final annotated dataset to a local folder. 
            Key features include footnote detection, preservation, and alignment during data processing, simplifying workflows for researchers and analysts.
